# RECURRING STYLE VIOLATIONS (S06 brand components)

| Violation | Correct form |
|---|---|
| `bg-white` hardcoded | `bg-background` or DS token |
| `transition-colors` | `transition-all` |
| `ring-2 ring-oem ring-offset-2` (v3) | `ring-[3px] ring-ring/50 focus-visible:outline-none` (v4) |
| Issue `#NNNN` in JSDoc/CSS | Strip — belongs in PR description |

